The application is changed frequently, hence the namespaces that are loaded into it usually have greater &quot;version&quot; than the incoming message. In this case, the application may have these namespaces which are different than the example message:
```
xmlns:cmn=&quot;https://www.services.zh.ch/uri/xmlns/zhs-common/1/5&quot;
